</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/indie/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_indie">Indie</a></li></ul></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6"><ul class="dropdown-nav-ul"><li ><a href="/book-reviews/ipad/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_ipad">iPad Book Apps</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/mystery-crime/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_mystery-crime">Mystery &amp; Crime</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/nature-travel/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_nature-travel">Nature &amp; Travel</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/psychology/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_psychology">Psychology</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/religion/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_religion">Religion</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/romance/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_romance">Romance</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/science-technology/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_science-technology">Science &amp; Technology</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/science-fiction-fantasy/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_science-fiction-fantasy">Science Fiction &amp; Fantasy</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/social-sciences/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_social-sciences">Social Sciences</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/thrillers/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_thrillers">Thrillers</a></li><li ><a href="/book-reviews/true-crime/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_true-crime">True Crime</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-sm-pull-8 col-md-4 col-md-pull-5"><div class="main-nav-header">BEST BOOKS</div><ul class="dropdown-nav-ul"><li ><a href="/book-reviews/stars/" id="KR_Navbar_Books_Stars">Kirkus Stars &amp; Recommendations</a></li></ul><div class="main-nav-header" style="margin-top: 16px;">BEST OF 2014</div><ul class="dropdown-nav-ul"><li><a href="/issue/best-of-2014/section/fiction/">Fiction</a></li><li><a href="/issue/best-of-2014/section/nonfiction/">Nonfiction</a></li><li><a href="/issue/best-of-2014/section/children/">Children's</a></li><li><a href="/issue/best-of-2014/section/teen/">Teen</a></li><li><a href="/issue/best-of-2014/section/indie/">Indie</a></li><li><a href="/issue/best-