            <div class="featured-book-title-ctr">
                <a id="KR_Featured_Title_2000139669_Title" class="featured-book-title-txt" href="/book-reviews/ame-dyckman/wolfie-the-bunny/">WOLFIE THE BUNNY</a>
                <br />
                
                    By
                    
                        
                            Ame Dyckman
                        
                    
                        
                            , Zachariah OHora
                        
                    
                
                <hr />
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="featured-book-review-ctr">
            <p>
                
                    
                        <span>Add to the growing collection of sibling stories, adoptive and otherwise, that delight and instruct. (artist's note, author's note) <i>(Picture book. 4-8)</i></span>
                    
                

                
