    <p>
        Our Indie program curates the self-published segment of the industry to help
        consumers and industry influencers discover books they may otherwise never find.
        <i><a id="KR_Home_AS_Editing_LearnMore" href="/author-services/indie/">Learn More&nbsp;&gt;</a></i>
